OL,7,FUniversity lecturers are set to be
OL,8,Fconsulted on industrial action
OL,9,Ffollowing what an education union
OL,10,Fdescribed as a "derisory" 1.4% pay
OL,11,Foffer.
OL,13,FMembers of the Educational Institute
OL,14,Fof Scotland University Lecturers'
OL,15,FAssociation (EIS ULA) are taking part
OL,16,Fin a consultative ballot on whether to
OL,17,Faccept the proposed offer, and whether
OL,18,Fthey back industrial action.
OL,20,FThe ballot will be open for six weeks
OL,21,Fand will close on August 11.
