OL,7,FThe EIS ULA, which is open to all
OL,8,Funiversity lecturers in Scotland, has
OL,9,Fcalled on its members to reject what
OL,10,Fit called a "real-terms pay cut" and
OL,11,Fback industrial action.
OL,13,FIt said the offer "fails to recognise"
OL,14,Fthe contribution made by university
OL,15,Flecturers, or make up for years of
OL,16,Fbelow-inflation pay rises.
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@`O]uD@SOUuD@fO]
