OL,5,Cpay offer
OL,7,F"Our members are working harder than
OL,8,Fever, delivering world-class education
OL,9,Fand research, yet their financial
OL,10,Fsecurity continues to be undermined by
OL,11,Femployers who appear unwilling to
OL,12,Foffer a fair deal.
OL,14,F"This offer fails to recognise the
OL,15,Fessential contributions of our members
OL,16,Fand does nothing to address the severe
OL,17,Fimpact of rising living costs or the
OL,18,Fsub-inflationary rises they have
OL,19,Fexperienced over a number of years."
