OL,7,FThe union said the offer stood in
OL,8,F"stark contrast" to the 4.14% increase
OL,9,Fgiven to further education lecturers,
OL,10,Fand to pay awards made to NHS workers
OL,11,Fand other public sector employees
OL,12,Facross Scotland.
OL,14,FIt said this disparity highlighted a
OL,15,F"clear injustice" within higher
OL,16,Feducation, and demonstrated the need
OL,17,Ffor a more equitable approach to staff
OL,18,Fpay,
